{"tid":2441860,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZONE 都解散啦仲出小分隊？簡直係垂死掙扎","createTime":"2021-03-11T03:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T08:26:34.000Z","uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bde67f2e0941fc4165ddc4b627b28cbc0adf5092","tid":2441860,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGUT5Fu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGUT5Fu.jpg&h=f87803a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZONE或將出小分隊<br />\n完整體解散&quot;的#IZONE商議小分隊活動的可能性<br />\n雖然IZ*ONE組合完全體將解散，但小分隊形式的活動可能性仍然存在。<br />\n11日，多位歌謠相關人士表示，IZ*ONE的部分成員和部分所屬社對IZ*ONE活動結束感到遺憾，因此部分成員們正在討論以小分隊的形式或其他項目組合進行活動的可能性。對於IZ*ONE中的部分成員組合進行活動正在積極討論中。 <br />\n但並不是說部分成員表現出了強烈的意志，小分隊或部分成員組合誕生的項目組合活動就能馬上順利進行。每位成員的所屬社不同，對於活動的意見也有分歧，因為CJ ENM是否將介入這個活動還有需要整理的部分遺留著。 <br />\n相關人士表示，IZ*ONE Project將在4月結束，如果CJ ENM不再介入，IZ*ONE部分成員組成小分隊繼續活動這件事上所屬社之間的意見將能夠更快地整理好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c06342048548556d81bbfe06aa11c56abf8f718","tid":2441860,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6aff189d3c926017a8be5e2f758972cbebf0459","tid":2441860,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"想用wizone換返izone返黎..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1273b46a731dbed7848e55df56155e4611581aab","tid":2441860,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6aff189d3c926017a8be5e2f758972cbebf0459","tid":2441860,"uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"